      • FieldDescriptor

        public FieldDescriptor(String id,
               String label,
               Class<? extends com.vaadin.ui.Field> fieldClass,
               Class<? extends com.vaadin.data.util.PropertyFormatter> formatterClass,
               int width,
               HorizontalAlignment valueAlignment,
               Class<?> valueType,
               Object defaultValue,
               boolean readOnly,
               boolean sortable,
               boolean required)
        Constructor for setting values of the FieldDefinition.
        Parameters:
        id - ID of the field.
        label - Label of the field.
        fieldClass - Field editor component or null.
        formatterClass - Field value formatter class.
        width - Width of the field.
        valueAlignment - Value vertical alignment.
        valueType - Type of the field value.
        defaultValue - Default value for field.
        readOnly - true if field is readonly.
        sortable - true if field is sortable.
        required - true if field is required.
